After installing ngrok using ngrok_docs (https://dashboard.ngrok.com/get-started/setup)

** quick shortcut for downloading ngrok ARM zip : "wget https://bin.equinox.io/c/4VmDzA7iaHb/ngrok-stable-linux-arm.zip"

# sudo nano /root/.ngrok2/ngrok.yml
add authtoken if not present already 
for adding tunnels 

`
authtoken: authtokensample
tunnels:
  ssh:
    proto: tcp
    addr: 22
  dashboard:
    proto: http
    addr: 8080
`